Masini manipur ibemma eigi apambadi jagatta hourakpada khwangda phi or una wana haibadi phanekki maongsi jagatta loina setli.adubu eikhoikhaktagi phanekki wakhalda khanduna khatnaribani.tasengbadi eikhoina khwaidagi thengna chaokhatpa tambada ojha saba yambadagi oikhibani.ngarisu madu mangai apumba potni .prithibida sa nga liraga chabagi heinabi chahi lising kayagi mamangdagi leiramlabani.sum chaokhatlakpadagi apat arak chaba toknakhibani.singjusu chap mannei morok sabada hakchang nungaitabadagi morok hantharaga salad onkhibani.ojha yammalle heiba heitaba .khangjadaba ojha mayamduna lila dramada yaoba dialogue.paramparagi matamga channadaba kayasi srmdokpa matam oire.nupimachasingna cycle thouduna school.tution chatpada phanekki mahutta salwar setpanadi cycle gi accident hanthagani khanjei.
